CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Cardio Diagnostics Holdings Inc is a biotechnology company that makes cardiovascular disease prevention and early detection more accessible, personalized, and precise. The company was formed to further develop and commercialize a proprietary artificial intelligence-driven integrated Genetic-Epigenetic EngineTM for cardiovascular disease to become the leading medical technology company for enabling improved prevention, early detection, and assists in the treatment of cardiovascular disease.
